songs.title: Kill This Club (Look Alive Demo)

Sremm Life
I'm so far out of sight
Catch a vibe
Sounds about right
Yeah, ayy, ayy, ayy, ayy
Ayy, ayy, ayy, hey, hey

Yeah, that sounds about right (sounds about right)
Kill this club, not my vibe (wait)

Look alive, look alive (look alive)

I can get you so right (yeah, so right)

[Chorus: Swae Lee]
Yup, I'm so far out of sight (yeah)
Yeah, that sounds about right (sounds about right, ayy)
